            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(SN) In nomine Domini. Millesimo C quadragesirno II, XIII kalendas marcii,
                        indicione V. <rs key="#Monasteries #Abbots">Cenobio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName>, sito inter Padum novem et veterem. Nos <persName
                            key="#childOf #Lombard #Offersio/donatio #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                                ><name ref="Rubeus de Guvernolo">Rubeo</name></persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/2418">Guvernulo</placeName>, <rs key="#childOf"
                            >filii</rs> quondam <persName key="#parentOf #Lombard"><name
                                ref="Wibertus de Plaza">Wiberti</name></persName> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/4165">Plaza</placeName>, et <persName
                            key="#Lombard #Offersio/donatio #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                                ><name ref="Gherardus f. Litterii">Gerardum</name></persName> filii
                            <persName key="#Lombard"><name ref="Litterius">Literii</name></persName>
                        et <persName
                            key="#siblingOf #childOf #Lombard #Offersio/donatio #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                                ><name ref="Bernardus">Bernardum</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#siblingOf #childOf #Lombard #Offersio/donatio #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                                ><name ref="Bruxatus">Bruxatum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf #Lombard">germanis</rs>, filii quondam <persName
                            key="#parentOf"><name ref="Walterius de Plaza"
                            >Vualterii</name></persName> de Plaza, *** qui professus sum ex nacione
                        nostra lege [vi]vere <rs key="#Lombard">Longobardorum</rs>, offertores et
                        donatores ipsius monasterii presentes presentibus diximus: quisquis in
                        sanctis ac in venerabilibus locis ex suis aliquid contulerit rebus iusta
                        hoctoris vocem, in hoc seculo centuplum accipiet, insuper, quod melius est,
                        vitam possidebit eternam. Ideoque nos supranorninati donamus et obferrimus a
                        presenti die in eadem monasterii, pro mercede anime nostre et parentum
                        nostrorum, tempore <persName key="#Abbots #Monasteries" ref="#people/3570"
                            >Wigelmi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs>, silicet <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals">pecies de terra aratoria</rs>
                        que iacet in <placeName
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Roads #Forests"
                            >Piscarola</placeName>. Fines: a mane <rs key="#Roads">via</rs>, a
                        meridie <placeName>Supragnacula</placeName>, a sera obfertores, de subto <rs
                            key="#Forests">bosco</rs>, sibi que sunt coerentes. Quas pecias supra ab
                        hac die eidem monasterio Sancti Benedicti donamus et offerrimus et per
                        presentem <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">cartam offersionis</rs> ibidem abendum
                        confirmamus sine nostra et heredum nostrorum contradicione. Equidem
                        spondimus atque promittimus: nos suprnc Rubeus et Gerardus et Bernardus et
                        Bruxatus, una cum nostris heredibus, iamscriptam cartam offersionis nostre
                        qualiter superius legitur in integrum ab omni homine defendere; quod si
                        defendere non potuerimus, aut si parti ipsius monasterii exinde aliquid per
                        quodvis ingenium subtraere quesierimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in
                            duplum</rs> eandem cartam parti ipsius monasterii restituamus in
                        consimili loco. Actum in loco <placeName ref="#places/2469"
                            >Campaniola</placeName>. Feliciter. + Signum manibus + <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Capo/de Lupi">Capo de
                                Lupi</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                                ><name ref="Sachello">Sachello</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio #childOf"><name ref="Albertus"
                                >Alberto</name></persName> filius <persName key="#parentOf"><name
                                ref="Arnaldus">Arnaldo</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Gandulfus/de Nuvelare"
                                >Gandulfo</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/462"
                            >Nuvelare</placeName> et <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                                ><name ref="Hubaldus/Palario">Ubaldo Palario</name></persName>
                        rogati sunt <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. + Signum manibus + Rubeus et
                        Gerardus et Bernardus et Bruxatus ***, qui hanc cartam offersionis fieret
                        firmare rogavit ut supra. + Signum + <rs key="#Writer">Scripsi</rs> ego
                            <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Gherardus"
                                >Gerardus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> sacri palacii post tradita complevi et dedi. </ab>
